io vem buscar a mulher, Celso encontra-os, enfurecido e drogado, e agride-os, ferindo a jovem." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="2921000" grandparentArt="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentRatingKey="687fff08c082969749e5c0d6" grandparentThumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20594_1672529-portrait.jpg" grandparentTitle="Piel Salvaje" grandparentType="show" index="99" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg" title="S01E099" userState="0"><Image alt="S01E099" type="coverArt" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E099" type="coverPoster" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/wedotv_amor_piel_salvaje20594_1672529-portrait.jpg"/><Image alt="S01E099" type="snapshot" url="https://d3dpwvkv1y8pcn.cloudfront.net/Images/S3/WAPIS/272_1672724.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1776656881" duration="2526000" endsAt="1776659407" id="69db90a7dbfffe597f0e9a06" onAir="1" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776677107" duration="2921000" endsAt="1776680028" id="69dce2a3d0c335321cdce4f3" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776698466" duration="2921000" endsAt="1776701387" id="69dce2a3d0c335321cdce4fa" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776719825" duration="2921000" endsAt="1776722746" id="69dce2a3d0c335321cdce501" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="7